Akhirnya ia berkomunikasi dengan salah satu perekrut bernama Biel. Amy yang menggunakan nama palsu Melody selama puluhan hari berakting seolah tertarik untuk hijrah ke Suriah demi mencari tahu teknik, metode dan proses perekrutan.
.
✍Film ini premier 2018 tapi baru dirilis global 2021 jadi jangan bingung ya. Film ini punya teknik seperti Searching, Host atau Unfriended, semua direkam bak rekaman layar desktop karakter utama. 
.
Jujur film ini bikin tegang dan punya hipnotis melihat bagaimana rentannya manusia yang terbuai kepada !$!$ dan gimana metode mereka yang bekerja maksimal. Kita akan melihat weapon, beheaded, stoned and killing atas nama Jihad. Melody perlahan terbuai yang malah buat kita ikut greget dan berharap she is okay during the process. Berani sekali dia. 

I can't explain more since this is a sensitive topic but I recommend this to you whoever wants to know about 'the recruitment' and avoid it. Be safe! Poin: 8.5/10.

Hi everyone. It has come to my attention that there are a couple of fake accounts impersonating my account. I posted about it in my stories because I loathe to dedicate a whole post and give oxygen to scammers who do not deserve the attention. But now that I have been alerted to a follower who gave her credit card details to the scammer and had to cancel her credit card, I feel I have to do everything in my power to warn others about the scammer accounts. 

1. Firstly, I am truly sorry for all of the inconvenience this has brought to you. It saddens me that a giveaway that I was excited about has turned into an opportunity for others to prey on the vulnerable.

2. If anyone ever asks you for credit card details/account details to enter a competition/win a prize, never give it.

3. Always check the IG handle carefully - my account is spelt ‘willtravelforfood17’ - the 2 scammer accounts I know of spelt theirs willtravellforfood17 and willtravelforfood17_

4. Block and report fake accounts when they come up - send me a DM if you are not sure if it is a fake account

5. I will only always have this 1 account so if any accounts request to follow you with a different name, it’s not me

Thank you and again, I am very sorry.
